### Habit Tracker API — click "Send Request" above each block
### (needs the VS Code extension: REST Client — humao.rest-client)
### Requests are separated by lines starting with ###

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### List all habits
GET {{baseUrl}}/habits

### Get one habit by id
GET {{baseUrl}}/habits/1

### Get a habit that doesn't exist (expect 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/habits/999

### Create a habit (expect 201)
POST {{baseUrl}}/habits
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "meditate"
}

### Create with empty name (expect 400 — Zod)
POST {{baseUrl}}/habits
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": ""
}

### Create with a wrong-type name (expect 400 — Zod)
POST {{baseUrl}}/habits
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": 123
}

### Update a habit — partial (expect 200)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/habits/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "done": true
}

### Update with wrong type (expect 400 — Zod)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/habits/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "done": "yes"
}

### Update a missing habit (expect 404 — P2025)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/habits/999
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "done": true
}

### Malformed JSON (expect 400 — error handler)
POST {{baseUrl}}/habits
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name": read }

### Delete a habit (expect 204, empty body)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/habits/1

### Delete a missing habit (expect 404)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/habits/999

### ─── Check-ins ───

### Log a check-in for habit 1 (expect 201) — run a few times
POST {{baseUrl}}/habits/1/checkins

### List habit 1's check-ins (expect array, newest first)
GET {{baseUrl}}/habits/1/checkins

### Check-in for a missing habit (expect 404)
POST {{baseUrl}}/habits/999/checkins
